            <description><![CDATA[【别生闷气！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E6%98%93%E5%BE%97%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E6%98%93%E5%BE%97%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女性情绪抑郁易得甲状腺疾病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】甲状腺疾病以女性偏多，专家提醒，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A730%E5%B2%81%E5%88%B060%E5%B2%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A730%E5%B2%81%E5%88%B060%E5%B2%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#甲状腺疾病多发于女性30岁到60岁#</span></a>。女性患上甲状腺疾病一是在情绪抑郁的时候，二是在青春发育期，第三是在孕期或产后六个月以内，最后是更年期。一些年轻女性在怀孕以后，出现了流产或胎停的情况，这和很多因素有关，甲状腺在其中占了一席之地，并且产生了很大的不良影响。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6NAwMXo" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
